				<div class="page__content pt-3 " id="booking">
					<h2 class="pt-3">HOW TO BOOK TABLE NOW?</h2>
					<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 1</p>
					<span>Choose the restaurant you want to go and  <b>Click </b> on the "Booking now" button </span>
					<img src="./img/booking1.PNG" class="img-fluid " alt="">
					<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 2</p>
					<span>Click on the icon <b>phone</b> </span> <br>
					<img src="./img/boooking2.PNG"class="img-fluid " alt="">
					<div class="grid">
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-6">
								<div class="grid__content">
									<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 3</p>
									<span>Enter full of your information in this <b>form</b> and click <b>"Đặt chỗ"</b>  button </span> <br>
									<img src="./img/booking3.PNG" class="img-fluid " style="height: 500px;" alt="">
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-6">
								<div class="grid__content">
									<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 4</p>
									<span>Click the <b>"cập nhập tài khoản"</b>  button</span> <br>
									<img src="./img/booking4.PNG" class="img-fluid" style="height: 300px;" alt="">
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>			
					<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 5</p>
					<span>Click the <b>"thông tin đơn hàng"</b> button to see your booking and Click <b>"Hủy"</b> if you want cancel book</span> <br>
					<img src="./img/booking5.PNG" class="img-fluid" alt="">
					<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 6</p>
					<span>Click the <b>"Đánh giá"</b> button to go to voting form and click <b>Submit</b> to add your rating for this restaurant </span> <br>
					<img src="./img/rating.PNG" class="img-fluid" alt="">
				</div>
		<!-- Favourite -->
