					<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 1</p>
					<span>Choose the restaurant you want to go and  <b>Click </b> on icon heart button </span> <br>
					<img src="./img/favourite1.PNG" class="img-fluid " style="height: 300px;" alt="">
					<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 2</p>
					<span>Click on the <b>"Danh sách yêu thích"</b> to go to the your favourite list. And click to icon heart to <b>remove</b> from this list</span> <br>
					<div class="grid">
