								<span>Click on the <b>"Design menu"</b><br>
								<img src="./img/design2.PNG" class="img-fluid alt=">
							</div>
							<div class=" col-md-9">
								<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 2</p>
								<span>Click on the <b>"Choose"</b> button to confirm design menu for this restaurant <br>
									<img src="./img/design3.PNG" class="img-fluid alt=">
							</div>
						</div>	
					</div>
					<p class="font-weight-bold">Step 3</p>
					<span>Choose type of food and enter full information foods. Then click <b>"ADD"</b> button to add food.
					Click <b>SAVE</b> to save the information foods and <b>CANCEL</b> to cancel adding food in menu </span> <br>
					<img src="./img/design4.PNG" class="img-fluid " alt="">	
